At Liv, we’re on a mission to elevate people’s level of living through enriched life experiences, deeper connections and unforgettable memories. Description: ShareMagnet offers rewards for individuals recommending and referring products and services to others across social networks.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Los Angeles Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: ShareMagnet, rewards customers for recommending and referring products and services to their friends and family across social networks.  Co-founded in 2010 by Thomas Larkin and Benjamin Stewart, the Company is focused on harnessing the social media power of companies’ best advertisers – their customers. Our guiding axiom is that word of mouth is the most trusted and effective form of all advertising. We believe that actual customers are the best marketers and, therefore, companies should hire them.  Retailers recognize this fact, however, the significant pain in the market has been how to effectively harness the power of word of mouth, track its ROI, and create a repeatable engagement structure.   ShareMagnet’s application Social Rebate incentivizes customers to share products and brands on social networks after a purchase is made. This allows for effective tracking of word of mouth efforts and clearly shows the ROI. Through a simple back-end integration, requiring no up-front fees and limited time commitment for most Ecommerce sites, customers are given the opportunity to rebate their purchase by sharing and promoting what they just bought with their online friends.  The application is fully integrated into all major social networks, including, Facebook, Twitter and Pinterest, and allows customers to login and post to their preferred social media site.  Each click of the link made by friends and family in the network rebates a portion of the original purchase back to the original customer.  The technology has a butterfly effect; secondary and tertiary purchasers can post a rebate link, too, which allows the client retailer to promote to a larger network and rebate additional customers. To date, SocialRebate has impressively shown over a 15% conversion rate for rebates posted to social media sites for participating brands.  This revenue is incremental to existing marketing and customer acquisition efforts, and only costs a client (defined as a retailer who has integrated SocialRebate onto its ecommerce platform) when a purchase has been made.  SocialRebate is currently installed with 100 clients, has processed over 20,000 transactions, has a 15% participation rate on referrals, and has currently developed software to integrate with the top ecommerce software platforms.  The retention rate for integrated clients is over 90% and on the customer side each new rebate claimed is a new registered user waiting to be re-targeted to or syndicated. Additionally, an estimated 20% of revenue generated has been from pre-purchases of Share Magnets, including brands such as MySpace, Care.com, National Positions, Okabashi and Gazelle.com.
Industry Groups: Advertising, Commerce and Shopping, Sales and Marketing

Description: Auto Transport Leads Provider
Headquarters Regions: Greater Denver Area, Western US
Full Description: LeadFi Auto Transport Leads is one of the leading companies in the auto transport industry that specializes in providing high-quality auto transport leads to transportation companies across the United States. With their exceptional service and track record of high conversion rates, they have become the top choice of transport businesses that are looking to expand their customer base and grow their business effectively. One of the key factors that set LeadFi Auto Transport Leads apart from the competition is their unwavering commitment to providing high-quality customer service. They understand the unique needs and requirements of transportation businesses, and they work closely with their clients to provide tailored solutions that meet their specific needs. In addition, LeadFi Auto Transport Leads has a robust network of industry-leading marketing professionals who work tirelessly to generate high-quality leads for their clients. They leverage cutting-edge technology and innovative marketing strategies to identify and target potential customers who are actively seeking auto transport services. Their high conversion rates are the result of their rigorous screening process that ensures that the leads they provide are of the highest quality. They only work with potential customers who are genuinely interested in auto transport services and are in a position to make a purchase. Furthermore, LeadFi Auto Transport Leads provides their clients with all the necessary tools and resources to effectively manage their leads and convert them into customers. They offer a comprehensive lead management system that allows clients to track their leads, communicate with potential customers, and manage their sales pipeline effectively. In conclusion, LeadFi Auto Transport Leads is a top-tier company that specializes in providing high-quality auto transport leads and high conversion rates to transportation businesses across the United States. Their commitment to excellence in customer service, marketing efficiency, and lead quality management has made them the preferred choice for companies looking to grow and expand their business in the auto transport industry. LeadFi is the leading provider of auto transport leads in the industry for over 20 years.  Auto transport leads are often overlooked, but they can be extremely lucrative. A great auto transport lead consists of a trucking company that specializes in shipping cars from point A to point B. This type of transporter usually charges a flat rate based on a distance traveled. They generally only ship vehicles between cities. However, they may offer interstate shipping services in some cases. The best auto transport leads are those that generate multiple phone calls per week from potential clients looking to ship their car(s). Car shipping leads are generated from various sources including classifieds websites, local newspapers, magazines, and even social media websites. They are usually used to generate quality traffic to your website. This kind of lead generation is usually done through paid advertising campaigns. However, auto transport leads are still considered to be one of the best types of leads. They are usually sent directly to the car shipper through CRM, email or phone calls. Car shipping leads are a great lead generation tool for car dealerships. They are a great way to generate qualified leads for your dealership. When someone buys a vehicle from you they usually want to ship their old vehicle back home. This means that they are going to need to transport their vehicle to their home. This is where car shipping leads come into play. With this type of lead, you can contact the person and offer to ship their vehicle back to them at a discounted rate. Car transport leads are generated when a potential client contacts you wanting to transport their vehicle. This could be anywhere around the world. Once you contact the person and explain what you do, you can offer them transportation services at a discounted price. A car transport lead is generated when a potential buyer wants to transport their vehicle to a different location. This could be anywhere in the world. So, when someone buys a vehicle from your dealership, they may decide to transport it somewhere else. This means that they will need to hire a trucking company to move their vehicle. This is where car transport leads come into play. You can contact the person and ask them if they would like to transport their vehicle. Then, you can offer them a discounted price to do so.

Description: Endless Electronics offers professional electronics repair services for iPads and iPhones.
Headquarters Regions: Midwestern US
Full Description: Endless Electronics offers professional electronics repair services.  At this time the company focuses on consumer electronics including Sony Playstation 3 Repair Services, Apple Iphone Repair Services, Microsoft Xbox 360 Repair Services and others. Many of the devices repaired by Endless Electronics are specialized consumer electronics. As more consumers shift from personal computers into mobile devices and console computing there is a growing demand for repair services providers for these devices.  Endless Electronics is capable of handling a diverse number of issues and repairs that plague modern devices. From replacing a broken iPhone screen to repairing a PCB board's SMT components on a Playstation 3 motherboard, Endless Electronics experience allows the company to offer a wide range of specialized repair services.  Endless Electronics is most known for their Sony Playstation 3 repair services. The PS3 experiences many issues including, the "Yellow Light of Death" aka YLOD, blu-ray diode replacements, power supply repair, and other less common issues. Our technicians specialize in fixing the error known as the YLOD or Yellow Light of Death. The most common source of this error is the solder joints under the RSX Chip (Graphics Chip). Endless Electronics has experience in repairing the solder joint that commonly fails. In addition the company offers various upgrades and modifications for the PS3 in order to fortify it against failure.  Endless Electronics is also know for their iPhone repair services. iPhones take a fair amount of wear and tear. The most common problem with the iPhone is damage to the LED screen. Endless Electronics has experience in replacing these screens and other delicate components inside the iPhone. For many users in a contract an iPhone repair services is much cheaper than buying a new iPhone out of contract without an upgrade credit. Thus, demand is growing for smart phone repair services.  Endless Electronics offers a one year warranty on all of their work and by the customer reviews, has a good reputation. Endless Electronics is continuing to grow and hopes to expand into industrial electronics repair in the near future.

Full Description: GoAnywhere Managed File Transfer is a  secure file transfer solution that allows organizations to secure and automate the exchange of data with their trading partners, customers, employees and internal systems.  GoAnywhere MFT streamlines and manages data movement through a centralized approach. It allows an organization to connect to almost any system (internal or external) and securely exchange data using a wide variety of standard protocols. With support for FTP, FTPS, SFTP, HTTP, HTTPS, AS2, SMTP, ZIP, multiple databases, error handling and more, GoAnywhere MFT can manage the complex business requirements related to securing and managing sensitive data transfers. GoAnywhere MFT allows external trading partners, customers and employees to to initiate and securely exchange files with the company.  GoAnywhere Managed File Transfer is controlled through an intuitive browser-based interface, and includes security features and audit trails for meeting internal security policies and complying with PCI DSS, HIPAA, GLBA and state privacy laws. GoAnywhere Gateway is both an enhanced reverse proxy and forward proxy, providing an an additional layer of network security when an organization needs to safely exchange data with its trading partners.  No incoming ports need to be opened into an organization's private/internal network and no sensitive information needs to be stored in the DMZ.
